## Journal articles

Ciunelis, K., Borkowski, R., & Błażkiewicz, M. (2024). The Impact of Induced Acceleration Perturbations in Selected Phases of the Gait Cycle on Kinematic and Kinetic Parameters. *Applied Sciences*, 14(11), 4849.\
[DOI: 10.3390/app14114849](https://doi.org/10.3390/app14114849)

## Research projects

**Synergy Project**\
Swedish School of Sport and Health Sciences (GIH), [Parasportakademin](https://www.gih.se/parasportakademin)\
PhD student in the Synergy project (since 2023), a collaboration between GIH Stockholm, the Swedish Parasport Academy, and AWF Warsaw. I took part in international data collections (Poland, Brazil), pilot studies, and project meetings (Belgium, Sweden). My doctoral dissertation, developed within the project, examines how ergonomic conditions affect trunk function and sport performance in wheelchair athletes.

**University Research Project No. 2**, AWF Warsaw\
Assessment of postural stability control in response to induced perturbations across age groups\
03.2023–12.2024

